You might want to try <code>cloning</code> the sheet before you populate it <br />
<div style="color:Black;background-color:White;"><pre>
$clonedSheet = <span style="color:Blue;">clone</span> $objPHPExcel-&gt;getActiveSheet();
</pre></div>then use <br />
<div style="color:Black;background-color:White;"><pre>
$objPHPExcel-&gt;addSheet($clonedSheet);
</pre></div>instead of<br />
<div style="color:Black;background-color:White;"><pre>
$objPHPExcel-&gt;createSheet(); 
 $objPHPExcel-&gt;load($inputFileName); 
</pre></div>
